com.bluegosling.concurrent

Class InterceptingExecutor.Interceptor.ListBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bluegosling.concurrent.InterceptingExecutor.Interceptor.ListBuilder
  • Enclosing interface:
    InterceptingExecutor.Interceptor

    public static class InterceptingExecutor.Interceptor.ListBuilder
extends Object
    Builds a list of interceptors. In addition to InterceptingExecutor.Interceptor instances, this allows the use of InterceptingExecutor.Decorator. Multiple adjacent InterceptingExecutor.Decorators will be collapsed into a single interceptor, to reduce the number of frames in the stack trace of an intercepted task.

    Interceptors and decorators for a given task are invoked in the order in which they are added.
